WEBVTT

00:02.628 --> 00:04.289
YOU'RE OKAY. IT'S OKAY.
[ CRYING ]

00:04.505 --> 00:06.041
NOW, LISTEN, LISTEN. I GOT ALL
OF YOUR CONTACT INFORMATION.

00:06.257 --> 00:07.872
RIGHT?
I DON'T WANT TO
COME WITH YOU.

00:08.092 --> 00:09.502
NO, YOU DON'T --
YOU DON'T HAVE TO COME WITH ME.

00:09.719 --> 00:12.677
JUST, AGAIN, TELL ME,
WHERE DID You SEE IT?

00:12.889 --> 00:15.130
ABOUT THREE KILOMETERS
DOWN THE CANYON.

00:15.349 --> 00:18.341
OKAY. OKAY.
YOU'RE OKAY.

00:18.561 --> 00:21.348
OKAY. OKAY.

00:21.564 --> 00:24.306
OKAY.

00:37.371 --> 00:39.327
[BRANCH CRACKS]
[ BIRD SQUAWKS]

00:51.886 --> 00:54.673
[WINGS FLAPPING,
BIRD SOUAWKING 1

01:11.572 --> 01:13.312
[ GASPS 1

01:16.786 --> 01:18.492
[ RETCHING 1

01:27.505 --> 01:31.339
[CELLPHONE RINGING]

01:31.551 --> 01:34.759
[ SIGHS, CLEARS THROAT ]

01:34.971 --> 01:37.178
[SIGHS]

01:37.390 --> 01:38.926
[SNIFFS]

01:39.141 --> 01:41.757
[COUGHS]

01:41.978 --> 01:43.388
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

01:43.604 --> 01:44.593
MORETTI.

01:44.814 --> 01:46.600
LONGMIRE: YOU UP?

01:46.816 --> 01:48.602
I AM NOW.

01:48.818 --> 01:50.683
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

02:02.957 --> 02:04.948
[ENGINE SHUTS OFF]

02:07.753 --> 02:09.539
RESIDENT SHOT OUT
HIS WINDOWS.

02:09.755 --> 02:11.131
HE'S DEMANDING TO SEE
THE SHERIFF.

02:11.340 --> 02:12.455
WHAT ARE YOU DOING
OUT HERE?

02:12.675 --> 02:13.960
I KNOW THE RESIDENT
IN QUESTION.

02:14.176 --> 02:15.302
I KNOW
IF I START RESPONDING

02:15.511 --> 02:16.876
EVERY TIME THIS GUY
MAKES A SCENE,

02:17.096 --> 02:18.302
THERE WILL BE
NO TURNING BACK.

02:18.514 --> 02:19.924
YOU CAN'T NEGOTIATE
WITH TERRORISTS.

02:20.141 --> 02:21.426
NOT THAT I'M COMPLAINING,

02:21.642 --> 02:23.928
BUT ISN'T FERG SUPPOSED TO BE
ON CALL THIS MORNING?

02:24.145 --> 02:26.932
HE'S ALREADY ON A CALL.
BUSY MORNING.

02:27.148 --> 02:28.604
SORRY TO PULL YOU AWAY
FROM HOME.

02:28.816 --> 02:30.807
PART OF THE JOB.

02:31.027 --> 02:33.018
SO, WHO'S THE WACKO?

02:33.237 --> 02:34.443
LUCIAN CONNALLY.

02:34.655 --> 02:36.270
CONNALLY?
AS IN BRANCH?

02:36.490 --> 02:37.900
HIS UNCLE.

02:38.117 --> 02:39.618
[ sc0|=|=s 1

02:47.501 --> 02:49.162
I NEED YOU
TO GO IN THERE.

02:49.378 --> 02:51.164
JUST DON'T TELL HIM
I'M HERE.

02:53.924 --> 02:55.630
IS HE DANGEROUS?

02:55.843 --> 02:57.629
OVER THE YEARS,
HE'S KILLED 10 MEN,

02:57.845 --> 02:59.381
BUT HE'S NEVER SHOT
A WOMAN.

03:16.280 --> 03:18.566
[GUNSHOT]
SON OF A BITCH!

03:23.412 --> 03:25.198
[GUN CLICKS]
HELLO, WALT.

03:26.165 --> 03:27.621
I THOUGHT YOU SAID HE WASN'T
GONNA SHOOT AT ME!

03:27.833 --> 03:29.334
I DIDN'T.
I SHOT THAT CHAIR.

03:29.543 --> 03:30.532
I'VE BEEN ASKING FOR TWO MONTHS
TO CHANGE MY MEDS.

03:30.753 --> 03:32.289
AIN'T NOBODY LISTENING TO ME.

03:32.505 --> 03:35.292
WHEN AIN'T NOBODY LISTENING,
YOU GOT TO TALK A LITTLE LOUDER!

03:35.508 --> 03:36.998
THERE AIN'T NOTHING
MUCH LOUDER

03:37.218 --> 03:38.958
THAN A 12-GAUGE
IN AN ENCLOSED SPACE.

03:39.178 --> 03:40.964
WHY AREN'T YOU
MARCHING THIS MAN

03:41.180 --> 03:43.262
OUT OF THE BUILDING
IN HANDCUFFS?
GOOD QUESTION.

03:43.474 --> 03:45.965
HOW ABOUT LUCIAN PAYS
FOR THE WINDOWS

03:46.185 --> 03:49.473
AND THE CHAIR AND PROMISES
NOT TO DO IT AGAIN?

03:49.689 --> 03:52.897
HE JUST DISCHARGED A WEAPON
IN A RETIREMENT HOME -- TWICE!

03:53.109 --> 03:55.065
THREE TIMES. TWO IN THE WINDOW,
ONE IN THE CHAIR.

03:55.277 --> 03:56.528
SEE, YOU WEREN'T
LISTENING.

03:56.737 --> 03:58.398
[CELLPHONE RINGS]
YEAH, FERG. WHAT'S up?

03:58.614 --> 04:01.606
HIKERS CALLED IT IN,

04:01.826 --> 04:05.239
BUT I HAD NO IDEA
IT WAS GONNA BE THIS BAD.

04:05.454 --> 04:07.319
[ BIRD SOUAWKING ]

04:15.005 --> 04:17.621
OH, WATCH YOUR STEP.

04:17.842 --> 04:22.176
THAT -- THAT VOMIT WASN'T HERE
WHEN I FIRST ARRIVED.

04:22.388 --> 04:24.845
GOD.
WHO WOULD DO THIS?

04:25.057 --> 04:28.800
NOT "WHO," "WHAT."

04:30.479 --> 04:31.685
LOOKS LIKE A BEAR ATTACK.

04:33.274 --> 04:35.481
A WALLET -- IT'S EMPTY.

04:35.693 --> 04:38.230
NOTHING IN THERE
BUT A STATE-ISSUED I.D.

04:38.446 --> 04:40.357
WEIRD, HUH?

04:40.573 --> 04:42.814
I ALREADY WENT THROUGH
ALL THE POCKETS.

04:46.871 --> 04:50.614
ED CRAWLEY.

04:50.833 --> 04:53.575
BORN IN '67.

04:53.794 --> 04:55.830
POWDER JUNCTION ADDRESS.

04:56.046 --> 04:57.252
HUH.

04:57.465 --> 05:01.208
CRYSTAL METH, A PIPE,
AND A LIGHTER.

05:01.427 --> 05:04.134
YOU KNOW, MAYBE THIS GUY
WAS PARTYING TOO HARD...
[CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS]

05:04.346 --> 05:06.382
...AND PASSED OUT IN
THE WRONG PART OF JELLYSTONE.

05:06.599 --> 05:08.214
DON'T OFTEN SEE
PEOPLE PARTYING

05:08.434 --> 05:11.141
THIS FAR AWAY
FROM EVERYTHING.

05:11.353 --> 05:13.139
ANY SIGN OF A VEHICLE?

05:13.355 --> 05:16.518
NOTHING BUT BEAR PAW PRINTS
AND SCAT.

05:16.734 --> 05:19.020
THESE WOUNDS COULD BE
INJECTION MARKS.

05:21.238 --> 05:23.729
YOU CAN'T...SHOOT METH.

05:23.949 --> 05:25.780
I MEAN, CAN YOU?

05:25.993 --> 05:28.780
YEAH, YOU CAN, BUT YOU DON'T
USUALLY SHOOT IT AND SMOKE IT.

05:28.996 --> 05:31.658
THIS GUY WAS LOOKING
TO REALLY PARTY.

05:36.253 --> 05:37.629
[SIGHS]

05:39.924 --> 05:42.006
ANYONE GOT A BAG?

05:42.218 --> 05:43.924
YOU'RE GROSS.

05:44.136 --> 05:46.218
I'M THOROUGH.

05:46.430 --> 05:50.298
VIC: YOU KNOW, I HAVE ARRESTED
MURDERERS AND RAPISTS.

05:50.518 --> 05:51.724
BUT A BEAR?

05:51.936 --> 05:53.392
MURDER IS MURDER.
WE GOT TO FIND THE KILLER.

05:53.604 --> 05:54.639
YOU'RE KIDDING, RIGHT?

05:54.855 --> 05:56.811
THE COMMUNITY
TENDS TO BE DEAD SERIOUS

05:57.024 --> 05:58.685
ABOUT BRINGING BEARS
TO JUSTICE.

05:58.901 --> 06:00.641
SO, HOW DO WE GET A WARRANT
FOR A BEAR?

06:00.861 --> 06:02.476
WE START BY TALKING
TO PETE BROOKS.

06:02.696 --> 06:04.311
WHO?

06:04.532 --> 06:06.614
DOCTORAL CANDIDATE
FROM THE UNIVERSITY.

06:06.826 --> 06:09.488
HE'S BEEN DOING A FIELD STUDY
ON THE BEAR POPULATION

06:09.703 --> 06:11.694
EAST OF THE
CONTINENTAL DIVIDE FOR --

06:11.914 --> 06:14.530
I DON'T KNOW -- THE LAST
SEVEN YEARS, EIGHT MAYBE.

06:14.750 --> 06:17.708
I FIGURE IF ANYONE CAN TELL US
ABOUT HOSTILE BEAR ACTIVITY

06:17.920 --> 06:21.754
IN THE AREA, IT'S PETE.

06:21.966 --> 06:23.206
[RINGING]

06:23.425 --> 06:24.835
PETE'S NOT ANSWERING.
HE'S UP IN THE BIGHORNS.

06:25.052 --> 06:26.212
SOMEONE REPORTED A GRIZZLY
UP THERE.

06:26.428 --> 06:28.043
THERE AREN'T ANY GRIZZLIES
IN THE BIGHORNS.

06:28.264 --> 06:30.550
I KNOW. BUT WOULDN'T IT BE
AMAZING IF THERE WERE?

06:30.766 --> 06:32.631
WELL, MISS, I'M GONNA
NEED You TO FIND PETE

06:32.852 --> 06:34.058
AND GET HIM BACK HERE.

06:34.270 --> 06:35.601
WE'VE GOT AN AGGRESSIVE BEAR
IN THE AREA,

06:35.813 --> 06:37.053
AND WE NEED TO FIND OUT

06:37.273 --> 06:38.888
IF THAT BEAR NEEDS RELOCATION
OR KILLING.

06:39.108 --> 06:41.349
YEAH, I DON'T KNOW. HE'S PRETTY
HARD TO REACH UP THERE.

06:41.569 --> 06:44.311
NOT WITH A SATELLITE PHONE,
IT ISN'T. KEEP TRYING.

06:44.530 --> 06:47.943
IN THE MEANTIME,
I'M GONNA CONTACT OMAR.

06:48.158 --> 06:50.649
WE CAN'T LET A BEAR
LIKE THIS RUN FREE.

06:57.167 --> 06:59.203
SHE SURE CLOUDED UP
WHEN YOU MENTIONED OMAR.

06:59.420 --> 07:01.081
WHAT ARE THEY,
A COUPLE OR SOMETHING?

07:01.297 --> 07:03.913
NO, THIS ORGANIZATION
HATES HUNTERS IN GENERAL,

07:04.133 --> 07:05.373
AND OMAR IN PARTICULAR.

07:05.593 --> 07:07.800
IN THEIR MIND, OMAR IS
THE WORST KIND OF HUNTER --

07:08.012 --> 07:09.718
A GOOD ONE.

07:11.432 --> 07:13.468
UNCLE LUCIAN,
JUST CALL MY DAD.

07:13.684 --> 07:16.847
HE'S GOT AT LEAST THREE
SPARE BEDROOMS IN THAT HOUSE.

07:17.062 --> 07:18.643
BRANCH, YOUR DADDY
COULD OPEN UP A WHOREHOUSE

07:18.856 --> 07:20.266
AND I'D STILL REFUSE
THE OFFER OF A BED.

07:20.482 --> 07:21.688
[LAUGHS]

07:21.901 --> 07:23.687
AT LEAST LET MY DAD
TALK TO THE RETIREMENT HOME.

07:23.903 --> 07:25.564
HE CAN GET THEM
TO DROP THE CHARGES.

07:25.779 --> 07:28.521
FACILITY.
IT AIN'T A HOME.

07:28.741 --> 07:29.730
IT'S A FACILITY.
[ SIGHS ]

07:29.950 --> 07:31.190
NEED ANYTHING, LUCIAN?

07:31.410 --> 07:33.321
NO, I'M FINE, RUBY.
THANK YOU.

07:33.537 --> 07:35.152
NOBODY FORCED YOU TO MOVE
INTO A RETIREMENT FACILITY.

07:35.372 --> 07:36.703
YOU CHECKED YOURSELF
IN THERE.

07:36.916 --> 07:39.157
YOU'RE DAMN RIGHT I DID.
I MAKE MY OWN CHOICES.

07:39.376 --> 07:41.241
I DON'T NEED MY BROTHER
PULLING STRINGS FOR ME.

07:41.462 --> 07:43.373
SO I'M GONNA SIT IN THIS CELL,
DRINK THIS COFFEE,

07:43.589 --> 07:45.454
PLAY THIS CHESS,
TAKE MY PUNISHMENT LIKE A MAN.

07:45.674 --> 07:50.759
BRANCH...
DON'T HARASS THE PRISONER.

07:50.971 --> 07:53.508
HEY, BRANCH.
I MET YOUR UNCLE EARLIER.

07:53.724 --> 07:56.306
HE'S GOT THAT TRADEMARK
CONNALLY CHARM.

07:56.518 --> 07:58.304
YOU GUYS FIND OUT ANYTHING
ABOUT THE VICTIM?

07:58.520 --> 07:59.680
YEAH.
HE'S A MURDERER.

07:59.897 --> 08:02.513
CRAWLEY'S AN EX-CON.
HE WAS SERVING 25 TO LIFE.

08:02.733 --> 08:05.520
BUT THEY LET HIM OUT TWO WEEKS
AGO -- GOOD BEHAVIOR.

08:05.736 --> 08:07.522
THE PAROLE BOARD SAID HE'S BEEN
LIVING WITH RELATIVES --

08:07.738 --> 08:09.353
PAM AND RUSSELL GREY.

08:09.573 --> 08:12.360
OKAY, YOU TWO LOOK INTO
ED CRAWLEY'S PRISON RECORDS.

08:12.576 --> 08:14.032
FIND OUT WHAT HE WAS LIKE
ON THE INSIDE.

08:14.244 --> 08:16.451
ASK AROUND AND SEE IF HE HAD
ANY FRIENDS OR KNOWN ASSOCIATES

08:16.664 --> 08:17.870
FROM HIS PAST IN TOWN.

08:18.082 --> 08:19.743
I'LL CHECK
THE TRIAL TRANSCRIPTS.

08:19.959 --> 08:21.199
FIND OUT WHO HE KILLED.

08:21.418 --> 08:23.204
IT WAS A LONG TIME AGO,
BUT SOME GRUDGES NEVER DIE.

08:23.420 --> 08:25.035
WANT ME TO TALK
TO CRAWLEY'S RELATIVES?

08:25.255 --> 08:28.418
NOPE, YOU GOT YOUR HANDS FULL
WITH YOUR UNCLE.

08:28.634 --> 08:29.965
I'LL DO IT.

08:30.177 --> 08:33.920
I GOT A STOP
TO MAKE FIRST.

08:34.139 --> 08:36.972
[MUSIC]

08:44.191 --> 08:48.685
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

08:54.618 --> 08:57.701
NICE OF YOU TO SHOW UP
TO YOUR FUNDRAISER.

08:57.913 --> 08:59.369
IS THAT WHAT THIS IS?

08:59.581 --> 09:01.788
BASED ON THE TURNOUT,
I MIGHT VOTE FOR THE OTHER GUY.

09:01.959 --> 09:03.824
HELPS IF THE CANDIDATE
ATTENDS.

09:04.044 --> 09:05.830
HENRY,
YOU KNOW WHAT THIS IS?

09:06.046 --> 09:08.913
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

09:13.721 --> 09:16.007
HEY! HEY!
NO, NO, NO, NO!

09:16.223 --> 09:17.963
THAT'S BAD MEAT.

09:18.183 --> 09:19.559
IT IS FLANK STEAK.

09:19.768 --> 09:22.384
THAT'S WHAT
I WAS AFRAID OF.

09:22.604 --> 09:24.890
WHY? WHAT IS SO BAD
ABOUT FLANK STEAK?

09:25.107 --> 09:26.438
NOTHING.

09:26.650 --> 09:30.563
UNLESS YOU TIE IT TO A GUY
TO TURN HIM INTO BEAR BAIT.

09:36.910 --> 09:37.990
OMAR.

09:38.203 --> 09:40.068
HENRY.

09:44.001 --> 09:45.491
WALT.

09:45.711 --> 09:46.996
HENRY.

09:49.506 --> 09:51.997
YOU'RE A HARD MAN
TO FIND.

09:54.053 --> 09:55.259
HEY, WALT.

09:55.471 --> 09:57.086
I'VE BEEN BACK COUNTRY,

09:57.306 --> 10:00.764
WATCHING A BUNCH OF RICH GUYS
FROM L.A. PRETEND TO HUNT.

10:00.976 --> 10:02.716
AND GROWING A BEARD.

10:02.936 --> 10:04.016
YEAH, IT'S A BIG LOOK
IN HOLLYWOOD.

10:04.229 --> 10:05.810
A LOT OF THE ACTORS
HAVE IT.

10:06.023 --> 10:08.560
WELL, YOU LOOK THE PART. I'M
GONNA NEED YOU TO GO BACK OUT.

10:08.776 --> 10:10.892
BEAR ATTACKED A GUY.

10:11.111 --> 10:12.647
HOW BAD IS IT?

10:12.863 --> 10:16.401
BAD ENOUGH TO KILL HIM.
I NEED YOU TO FIND THAT BEAR.

10:16.617 --> 10:18.153
ISN'T THIS USUALLY
THE TERRITORY

10:18.368 --> 10:20.404
OF THAT BEAR-HUGGER,
ECO-MANIAC PETE BROOKS?

10:20.621 --> 10:22.282
PETE'S NOT AROUND.
I NEED YOU.

10:22.498 --> 10:25.365
GENTLEMEN,
HOW IS EVERYTHING?

10:25.584 --> 10:26.790
GREAT.

10:27.002 --> 10:29.209
JUST LET ME KNOW IF I CAN
GET YOU ANYTHING --

10:29.421 --> 10:31.707
COFFEE, A CONSCIENCE.

10:31.924 --> 10:33.539
HENRY.
WALT.

10:33.759 --> 10:34.874
HUNTING THIS BEAR --

10:35.094 --> 10:36.209
I'M JUST TRYING TO
LOCATE THE BEAR.

10:36.428 --> 10:37.838
WE HADN'T EVEN
TALKED PRICE YET.

10:38.055 --> 10:39.386
WHERE'D THE ATTACK HAPPEN?

10:39.598 --> 10:41.008
ABOUT SEVEN MILES NORTHWEST
OF TOWN.

10:41.225 --> 10:42.840
RIGHT WHERE
THE BEAR SHOULD BE.

10:43.060 --> 10:44.425
WHY PUNISH THIS BEAR?

10:44.645 --> 10:45.851
IT WOULD BE LIKE PUNISHING
THE WIND FOR BLOWING.

10:46.063 --> 10:48.304
AND IF THE WIND
KILLED A MAN?

10:48.524 --> 10:49.764
I GOT NO OTHER OPTION,
HENRY.

10:49.983 --> 10:52.599
YES, YOU DO.

10:52.820 --> 10:54.685
[COFFEE POT THUDS]

10:57.699 --> 10:58.734
CAN YOU PAY ME?

10:58.951 --> 11:00.816
NO.

11:01.036 --> 11:02.742
WELL,
I'LL MAKE YOU A DEAL.

11:02.955 --> 11:04.866
I'LL HELP YOU
TRACK THIS BEAR,

11:05.082 --> 11:07.698
BUT YOU GOT TO LEND ME
ONE OF YOUR DEPUTIES.

11:07.918 --> 11:09.328
LET ME GUESS.
IT'S NOT FERG.

11:09.545 --> 11:11.331
NO.

11:11.547 --> 11:14.380
I WANT
THAT FEISTY ITALIAN.

11:14.591 --> 11:17.628
CAREFUL
WHAT YOU WISH FOR.

11:23.267 --> 11:26.805
WELL, WHAT A SURPRISE.

11:27.020 --> 11:29.762
PAM! GUESS WHO'S HERE!

11:29.982 --> 11:32.348
YOU GOT A MINUTE TO TALK?

11:32.568 --> 11:35.560
SURE.
I'M ASSUMING THIS IS ABOUT ED.

11:35.779 --> 11:37.189
WHAT'D HE DO?

11:37.406 --> 11:40.068
HE GOT MAULED TO DEATH
BY A BEAR.

11:42.119 --> 11:44.405
I CAN'T BELIEVE IT.

11:44.621 --> 11:46.077
A BEAR?

11:46.290 --> 11:48.622
YOUR BROTHER GAVE THIS
AS HIS ADDRESS.

11:48.834 --> 11:50.995
WAS HE STAYING WITH YOU?
YEAH.

11:51.211 --> 11:53.873
HE REALLY DIDN'T HAVE
NO OTHER OPTIONS.

11:54.089 --> 11:55.295
HE WAS ONLY
SUPPOSED TO STAY HERE A WEEK.

11:55.507 --> 11:57.839
TWO WEEKS LATER,
NO JOB, NO APARTMENT.

11:58.051 --> 11:59.507
YOU DIDN'T WANT ED
STAYING HERE?

11:59.720 --> 12:00.960
GUY'S A CRIMINAL.

12:01.180 --> 12:04.047
BEST THING THAT EVER HAPPENED
TO PAM AND HER FOLKS

12:04.266 --> 12:05.631
WAS ED GOING TO PRISON.

12:05.851 --> 12:08.684
SO, UH, EITHER OF YOU
HAVE ANY IDEA

12:08.896 --> 12:11.478
WHAT ED WAS DOING
IN THE WOODS?

12:11.690 --> 12:13.226
I DON'T KNOW.

12:13.442 --> 12:17.151
HE, UH, WASN'T TOO INTERESTED
IN HIKING OR THE OUTDOORS.

12:17.362 --> 12:19.853
LAST I SAW OF HIM, HE WAS GOING
ON A JOB INTERVIEW.

12:20.073 --> 12:22.485
SAID HE GOT A LEAD FROM ONE
OF HIS PRISON BUDDIES.

12:22.701 --> 12:25.443
THIS PRISON BUDDY --
ED GIVE YOU A NAME?

12:25.662 --> 12:27.072
I DIDN'T ASK FOR ONE.

12:27.289 --> 12:30.452
TO BE HONEST, I THOUGHT THE
WHOLE JOB THING WAS BULLSHIT.

12:30.667 --> 12:33.249
I FIGURED HE WAS GETTING HIGH
OR SOMETHING.

12:33.462 --> 12:36.044
WAS ED USING DRUGS?
NO.

12:36.256 --> 12:38.872
HE WAS PRETTY SCARY
WHEN HE WAS USING.

12:39.092 --> 12:40.878
I DIDN'T SEE NONE OF THAT
WHEN HE WAS HERE.

12:41.094 --> 12:42.470
DAMN IT!

12:42.679 --> 12:45.546
I LET HIM BORROW MY OLD TACOMA
FOR THAT JOB INTERVIEW.

12:45.766 --> 12:46.881
DID YOU FIND IT?

12:47.100 --> 12:48.385
I'M SORRY, NO.

12:48.602 --> 12:52.140
BUT IF YOU GIVE ME A DESCRIPTION
OF THE VEHICLE,

12:52.356 --> 12:53.345
WE'LL DO OUR BEST
TO FIND IT FOR YOU.

12:53.565 --> 12:55.726
EVEN DEAD
HE'S A PAIN IN MY ASS.

12:55.943 --> 12:58.525
I'LL GET YOU A COPY
OF MY REGISTRATION.

12:58.737 --> 13:01.353
SORRY ABOUT RUSSELL.

13:01.573 --> 13:04.280
HE'S BEEN...
PRETTY UPSET LATELY.

13:04.493 --> 13:06.859
THEY CUT HIS HOURS
WAY BACK.

13:07.079 --> 13:11.368
PLUS HE -- HE DIDN'T KNOW
THE GOOD ED -- FROM BEFORE.

13:13.335 --> 13:16.202
[VOICE BREAKING ] HE WAS SUCH
A SWEET LITTLE KID.

13:16.421 --> 13:18.833
[CRIES]

13:19.049 --> 13:21.756
I CAN'T BELIEVE
HE'S GONE.

13:24.388 --> 13:25.503
I UNDERSTAND.

13:25.722 --> 13:27.838
NOW, APART FROM THE BUDDY
FROM PRISON,

13:28.058 --> 13:31.221
DID ED HOOK UP WITH ANY
OLD FRIENDS THAT YOU KNOW OF?

13:31.436 --> 13:32.551
[ SCOFFS ]

13:32.771 --> 13:33.977
ALL HIS OLD FRIENDS ARE DEAD
OR IN JAIL.

13:34.189 --> 13:35.395
WHAT ABOUT ENEMIES?

13:35.607 --> 13:38.815
ENEMIES? ED?

13:39.027 --> 13:42.019
WHAT ABOUT THE PARENTS
OF THAT GIRL HE KILLED?

13:44.032 --> 13:45.613
[ SNIFFLES ]

14:02.426 --> 14:04.917
HEY, WALT.

14:05.137 --> 14:06.923
RU BY.

14:07.139 --> 14:08.549
OH, BRANCH LEFT THIS
FOR YOU --

14:08.765 --> 14:11.017
RECORDS ON ED CRAWLEY'S
MURDER TRIAL.

14:11.226 --> 14:14.013
HE ALSO HAD ME CALL DOWN
TO THE STATE PENITENTIARY

14:14.229 --> 14:15.594
TO HAVE THE WARDEN
SEND OVER A LIST

14:15.814 --> 14:19.272
OF ALL THE MEN
HE'S BEEN LOCKED UP WITH.

14:19.484 --> 14:20.894
THANK YOU, RUBY.
MM-HMM.

14:21.111 --> 14:22.726
WHEN YOU, UH,
TALK TO BRANCH NEXT,

14:22.946 --> 14:24.732
COULD YOU,
UH, LET HIM KNOW

14:24.948 --> 14:26.563
I NEED A LITTLE BACKGROUND
ON RUSSELL GREY,

14:26.783 --> 14:27.738
CRAWLEY'S
BROTHER-IN-LAW?

14:27.951 --> 14:29.452
RUSSELL GREY.

14:31.580 --> 14:33.286
FERG,
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

14:33.498 --> 14:36.114
SHERIFF CONNALLY WANTED TO HELP
OUT WITH THE INVESTIGATION.

14:36.335 --> 14:37.950
MR. CONNALLY
IS NO LONGER THE SHERIFF.

14:38.170 --> 14:39.660
HE'S UNDER ARREST
PENDING ASSAULT CHARGES

14:39.880 --> 14:40.960
FROM THE RETIREMENT HOME.

14:41.173 --> 14:43.004
OUR INVESTIGATION
IS NONE OF HIS BUSINESS.

14:43.216 --> 14:45.047
HEY, WALT, DID YOU SEE THE MARK
ON THAT BOY'S ANKLES?

14:45.260 --> 14:46.375
HE WAS RESTRAINED.

14:46.595 --> 14:47.584
I SAW IT, LUCIAN.

14:47.804 --> 14:48.793
HE WAS A DRUGGIE, TOO.

14:49.014 --> 14:50.470
WE DID FIND
SOME CRYSTAL METH

14:50.682 --> 14:52.889
AND WHAT COULD BE INJECTION
MARKS ON CRAWLEY'S LEGS.

14:53.101 --> 14:54.352
BUT WE WON'T KNOW
IF HE WAS USING

14:54.561 --> 14:56.347
UNTIL WE DO THE AUTOPSY
AND GET A TOX SCREEN BACK.

14:56.563 --> 14:57.552
WHO YOU LOOKING AT HERE?
EVERYBODY.

14:57.773 --> 14:59.764
OH, COME ON, WALT.

14:59.983 --> 15:01.974
FERG, THE VICTIM WAS LAST SEEN
IN HIS BROTHER-IN-LAW'S TACOMA.

15:02.194 --> 15:04.435
HERE'S THE REGISTRATION.
I WANT YOU TO FIND THAT CAR.

15:04.654 --> 15:05.780
[ DOOR OPENS ]
ON IT.

15:05.989 --> 15:07.104
WHAT ABOUT THAT
NO-GOOD NEPHEW OF MINE?

15:07.324 --> 15:08.188
WHY AIN'T THAT LITTLE TURD HERE
HELPING OUT?

15:08.408 --> 15:09.818
I AM HELPING.

15:10.035 --> 15:12.492
I'M BRINGING OUR PAIN-IN-THE-ASS
PRISONER HIS TACOS.

15:12.704 --> 15:14.205
RUBY, NEED YOU TO FIND ME
AN ADDRESS --

15:14.414 --> 15:15.699
DONNA AND IRA CRAIG.

15:15.916 --> 15:16.905
WHO'S DONNA
AND IRA CRAIG?

15:17.125 --> 15:19.411
NONE OF YOUR BUSINESS.
HEY, WALT.

15:21.630 --> 15:25.418
YOU OWE ME $6.95
PLUS TIP.

15:31.431 --> 15:35.219
VICTIM WAS FOUND DOWN THAT PATH
ABOUT A MILE OR SO.

15:41.108 --> 15:43.975
YOU MAKE A HABIT OF LEERING
AT MARRIED WOMEN SO BLATANTLY?

15:44.194 --> 15:48.403
WELL, FIRST OF ALL...
YES.

15:48.615 --> 15:52.608
SECONDLY, I HAD NO IDEA
YOU WERE MARRIED.

15:52.828 --> 15:55.240
YOU DON'T
SEEM DOMESTICATED.

15:55.455 --> 15:56.865
YOU REALLY THINK YOU
WANT TO TALK TO ME LIKE THAT

15:57.082 --> 15:58.197
WHEN I'M HOLDING THIS?

16:01.002 --> 16:02.208
I JUST DON'T KNOW WHY
YOU DON'T HAVE THE COURTESY

16:02.421 --> 16:03.456
TO WEAR A RING.

16:03.672 --> 16:05.378
AT LEAST WAFFLES
WEARS A COLLAR.

16:05.590 --> 16:06.625
WHO'S WAFFLES?

16:06.842 --> 16:07.877
THE KILLER BEAR.

16:08.093 --> 16:09.333
HER NAME'S WAFFLES.

16:09.553 --> 16:12.590
THEY PUT A TRACKING COLLAR
ON HER A YEAR AGO

16:12.806 --> 16:14.342
SO THEY COULD STUDY HER.

16:14.558 --> 16:17.721
I'VE TRACKED HER ONLINE.
IT'S PRETTY HANDY.

16:17.936 --> 16:20.177
BUT IT SURE TAKES THE FUN
OUT OF HUNTIN'.

16:20.397 --> 16:23.309
WE'RE SUPPOSED TO BE TRAPPING
THE BEAR, NOT HUNTING IT.

16:23.525 --> 16:24.765
WELL, THAT'S THE IDEA.

16:24.985 --> 16:27.522
BUT WE GOT TO BE READY
FOR THE POSSIBILITY

16:27.737 --> 16:30.319
THAT WAFFLES WON'T GO ALONG
WITH OUR PLAN.

16:30.532 --> 16:34.400
BUT DON'T WORRY, VICKI.
OMAR WILL PROTECT YOU.

16:36.329 --> 16:38.706
WHY ARE YOU
TELLING US THIS?

16:38.915 --> 16:40.746
ARE WE SUPPOSED
TO FEEL BAD?
NO.

16:40.959 --> 16:43.120
NO, IT, UH,
SEEMED LIKE SOMETHING

16:43.336 --> 16:44.621
YOU MIGHT LIKE TO KNOW.

16:44.838 --> 16:47.204
YOU HAVE ANY CHILDREN,
SHERIFF LONGMIRE?

16:47.424 --> 16:49.961
YES, I DO.
I HAVE A DAUGHTER.

16:50.177 --> 16:53.544
OH. WELL, THIS IS
OUR DAUGHTER, BLAIR.
HONEY.

16:53.763 --> 16:55.503
SHE SHOULD BE 37 YEARS OLD
RIGHT NOW.

16:55.724 --> 16:57.885
IT'S AN ARTIST'S PROJECTION
OF WHAT SHE WOULD LOOK LIKE.

16:58.101 --> 16:59.966
WE HAVE ONE PAINTED EVERY YEAR
ON HER BIRTHDAY.

17:00.187 --> 17:02.348
THAT'S ALL WE HAVE LEFT
OF OUR DAUGHTER,

17:02.564 --> 17:05.522
AFTER ED CRAWLEY
STABBED HER 12 TIMES.

17:05.734 --> 17:08.146
YOU KNOW, HIS LAWYERS SAID
HE WASN'T IN HIS RIGHT MIND

17:08.361 --> 17:09.976
BECAUSE OF THE DRUGS.

17:10.197 --> 17:13.485
BUT A HUMAN BEING DOES NOT STAB
A 17-YEAR-OLD GIRL 12 TIMES,

17:13.700 --> 17:14.906
DRUGS OR NO DRUGS.

17:15.118 --> 17:16.574
NO, ED CRAWLEY
WAS A MONSTER.

17:16.786 --> 17:18.742
DONNA, HONEY, LET IT GO.
AND IF IT WERE UP TO ME,

17:18.955 --> 17:20.946
HE WOULD HAVE BEEN SWINGING
FROM A ROPE YEARS AGO.

17:21.166 --> 17:25.159
WHAT IS THE POINT OF CAPITAL
PUNISHMENT IF WE CAN'T USE IT?!

17:25.378 --> 17:28.245
IRA: YOU'VE GOT TO
UNDERSTAND, SHERIFF.

17:28.465 --> 17:29.921
FOR THE LAST 20 YEARS,

17:30.133 --> 17:32.215
WE'VE BEEN WORKING TO KEEP
BLAIR'S KILLER IN PRISON.

17:32.427 --> 17:33.507
WE WRITE LETTERS.

17:33.720 --> 17:35.130
WE SHOW UP
AT HIS PAROLE HEARINGS.

17:35.347 --> 17:36.587
IF YOU DON'T MIND MY ASKING,

17:36.806 --> 17:38.091
WHEN WAS THE LAST TIME
YOU SAW THE VICTIM?

17:38.308 --> 17:41.596
"VICTIM"?
NOW HE'S THE VICTIM?

17:41.811 --> 17:45.019
IRA: WE WERE AT HIS LAST
PAROLE HEARING.

17:45.232 --> 17:47.564
DID YOU HAVE ANY CONTACT
WITH HIM THEN?
YES, SHERIFF.

17:47.776 --> 17:49.812
WE YELLED. WE CURSED.
WE MADE OUR FEELINGS KNOWN.

17:50.028 --> 17:51.268
AND STILL
THEY RELEASED HIM.

17:51.488 --> 17:53.319
IT -- IT TOOK A BEAR

17:53.532 --> 17:56.114
TO DO WHAT THE SO-CALLED
JUSTICE SYSTEM SHOULD HAVE DONE.

17:56.326 --> 17:57.611
THE HEARING WAS A SHAM.

17:57.827 --> 18:00.034
THE NEW WARDEN DIDN'T KNOW
ANYTHING ABOUT THE CASE.

18:00.247 --> 18:02.579
NOW, IF THE OLD WARDEN,
DAN BLACKBURN, HAD BEEN THERE,

18:02.791 --> 18:04.327
HE WOULD HAVE CONVINCED
THAT BOARD

18:04.543 --> 18:06.158
TO KEEP THAT ANIMAL
IN PRISON.

18:06.378 --> 18:08.460
WHAT'S GONNA HAPPEN
WITH THE BEAR?

18:08.672 --> 18:11.288
EEEIEE

18:11.508 --> 18:14.090
COULD BE RELOCATED.
COULD BE PUT DOWN.

18:14.302 --> 18:16.338
OUGHT TO GET A MEDAL.

18:24.187 --> 18:26.849
RUBY,
THIS IS UNIT 4, OVER.

18:27.065 --> 18:29.306
HELLO, FERG.

18:29.526 --> 18:31.562
RUBY, I CANVASSED
THE LOCAL TAVERNS.

18:31.778 --> 18:34.019
UH, IT'S A NEGATIVE
ON THE VICTIM'S CAR.

18:34.239 --> 18:36.230
OKAY.

18:36.449 --> 18:39.657
FREQUENTLY THAT'S WHERE
THESE EX-CONS HANG.

18:39.869 --> 18:42.702
THAT'S WHAT THEY SAID
AT THE SEMINAR WALT SENT ME TO.

18:42.914 --> 18:44.745
mm

18:49.170 --> 18:50.876
OKAY, THEN.

18:51.089 --> 18:52.078
FERG OUT.

18:52.299 --> 18:53.755
ALL RIGHTY, FERG.

18:53.967 --> 18:55.832
[BIRDS CHIRPING]

19:14.696 --> 19:16.482
[ BEAR GROWLS ]

19:19.242 --> 19:20.527
KEEP BEHIND ME.

19:20.744 --> 19:22.735
NOW, DON'T PANIC
IF THE BEAR CHARGES US.

19:22.954 --> 19:25.741
NOW, IF A BULLET WON'T STOP HIM,
THIS WILL SLOW HIM DOWN.

19:25.957 --> 19:27.163
OKAY.
ALL RIGHT?

19:27.375 --> 19:28.364
[ DART GUN HISSES]

19:28.585 --> 19:30.792
[ GROANING ]

19:31.004 --> 19:32.710
WHO'S IN THERE?!

19:32.922 --> 19:34.913
PETE: DON'T SHOOT!

19:35.133 --> 19:36.543
OH, NO.

19:36.760 --> 19:37.749
OH, NO, NO.

19:37.969 --> 19:39.175
I'M SO SORRY.
I DIDN'T MEAN --

19:39.387 --> 19:41.173
I WAS AIMING
FOR THE BEAR.

19:41.389 --> 19:43.129
PETE? YOU MORON!

19:43.350 --> 19:44.339
YOU JUST SHOT
A SHERIFF'S DEPUTY!

19:44.559 --> 19:45.844
I WAS AIMING
FOR THE BEAR!

19:46.061 --> 19:47.267
A BEAR?! WHAT KIND OF BEAR?!
A BLONDE BEAR?!

19:47.479 --> 19:48.685
IT WAS AN ACCIDENT!

19:48.897 --> 19:50.683
WELL, NOW THE DAMN
KILLER BEAR IS GONE!

19:50.899 --> 19:54.107
YEAH, WHAT WERE YOU THINKING,
YOU STUPID MOTHER--

19:54.319 --> 19:56.935
AAH!

19:57.155 --> 19:58.565
[ PANTING ]

19:58.782 --> 20:00.192
VICKI. VICKI.

20:04.871 --> 20:05.906
YOU LET DEPUTY MORETTI
GET SHOT.

20:06.122 --> 20:07.328
WELL,
ONLY WITH A TRANOUILIZER.

20:07.540 --> 20:08.700
AND IT'S ONLY A SMALL DART.
SHE'S GONNA BE FINE.

20:08.917 --> 20:10.077
NOT ABOUT THE SIZE
OF THE DART, PETE.

20:10.293 --> 20:11.408
YOU SHOT MY DEPUTY.

20:11.628 --> 20:13.118
SHE WASN'T EVEN WEARING
A HUNTING VEST.

20:13.338 --> 20:15.545
WALT, THIS NUT SHOT
AT US ON PURPOSE

20:15.757 --> 20:17.088
BECAUSE HE THOUGHT WE WERE OUT
TO KILL THAT BEAR.

20:17.300 --> 20:18.915
WELL, WEREN'T YOU?
WELL, YEAH, OF COURSE!

20:20.387 --> 20:21.672
WAFFLES
DOESN'T KILL HUMANS.

20:21.888 --> 20:23.003
SHE'S ALREADY GOT
TWO STRIKES.

20:23.223 --> 20:24.383
THOSE WERE JUST
LIVESTOCK KILLS.

20:24.599 --> 20:26.260
SHE DOES NOT DESERVE TO BE
EUTHANIZED FOR THIS!

20:26.476 --> 20:27.886
WALT, LOOK,
I KNOW THIS BEAR'S BEHAVIOR.

20:28.103 --> 20:29.434
I'VE BEEN MONITORING HER
FOR MONTHS.

20:29.646 --> 20:31.136
SHE'S A GOOD BEAR.
PETE, SHE KILLED A MAN.

20:31.356 --> 20:32.766
BUT YOU HAVE NO PROOF
OF THAT.

20:32.982 --> 20:34.973
JUST LET ME -- LET ME TEST
HER HAIR FOR ISOTOPES.

20:35.193 --> 20:36.979
IF SHE CONSUMED HUMAN FLESH,
IT'LL SHOW UP.

20:37.195 --> 20:39.436
BUT I BELIEVE
THAT IT WON'T.

20:39.656 --> 20:41.066
WALT, LOOK, ARREST HIM,

20:41.282 --> 20:42.613
OR AT LEAST HAVE
HIS LICENSE REVOKED.
WHAT LICENSE?

20:42.826 --> 20:45.033
I DON'T KNOW. HIS
GRANOLA-SON-OF-A-BITCH LICENSE!

20:45.245 --> 20:46.860
PROVING THIS WAS ANYTHING MORE
THAN AN ACCIDENT

20:47.080 --> 20:48.286
IS GONNA BE
PRETTY DIFFICULT, OMAR,

20:48.498 --> 20:49.829
PARTICULARLY
CONSIDERING THE VIC

20:50.041 --> 20:52.202
WASN'T WEARING ANY
BRIGHT ORANGE SAFETY CLOTHING.

20:52.419 --> 20:53.909
WAS SHE, OMAR?

20:54.129 --> 20:55.710
NOW, IF YOU IDIOTS
WILL EXCUSE ME,

20:55.922 --> 20:57.708
I THINK I'LL GO IN
AND SEE THE PATIENT.

20:57.924 --> 21:00.415
YOU WANT ME TO COME,
TOO?
NO!

21:04.222 --> 21:07.089
SO, HOW'D YOU LIKE
YOUR FIRST HUNTING TRIP?

21:07.308 --> 21:09.469
THIS WAS NOT
IN THE BROCHURE.

21:09.686 --> 21:12.143
WOULD YOU LIKE ME
TO CALL YOUR HUSBAND?
WHY?

21:12.355 --> 21:15.563
HE'S OUT OF TOWN AGAIN.
[SNIFFS]

21:15.775 --> 21:17.356
I DON'T WANT HIM
TO KNOW ANYWAY.

21:17.569 --> 21:19.434
VIC, HE'D PROBABLY
WANT TO KNOW.

21:19.654 --> 21:22.441
HE DOESN'T CARE.

21:22.657 --> 21:25.069
WE GOT IN A FIGHT.
AGAIN.

21:25.285 --> 21:27.992
WE FIGHT ALL THE TIME,
WALT.

21:28.204 --> 21:30.820
EVER SINCE HE DRAGGED MY ASS
HERE FROM PHILADELPHIA.

21:31.040 --> 21:33.747
VIC, THIS IS REALLY
NONE OF MY BUSINESS.

21:33.960 --> 21:38.374
YESTERDAY AT BREAKFAST,
HE -- HE INFORMED ME --

21:38.590 --> 21:40.581
INFORMED ME...

21:40.800 --> 21:44.008
THAT HE WAS THINKING
ABOUT TAKING ANOTHER TRANSFER.

21:44.220 --> 21:46.632
STUPID GAS COMPANY
WANTS TO PROMOTE HIM AGAIN.

21:46.848 --> 21:49.260
THEY WANT HIM
TO MOVE TO AUSTRALIA.

21:49.476 --> 21:52.684
I CAN'T BE A COP
IN AUSTRALIA.

21:52.896 --> 21:55.103
WELL [CHUCKLES]
YOU'VE NEVER EXACTLY TOLD ME

21:55.315 --> 21:57.271
THAT YOU LOVE IT
HERE IN WYOMING, SO...

21:57.484 --> 21:59.099
OH, I HATE IT.

21:59.319 --> 22:01.685
BUT DON'T YOU THINK
HE SHOULD HAVE ASKED?

22:01.905 --> 22:03.520
I MEAN,
WHAT WOULD YOU HAVE DONE?

22:03.740 --> 22:06.072
WELL, I'M A DIFFERENT MAN
THAN YOUR HUSBAND, SO...

22:06.284 --> 22:09.947
YOU'RE DIFFERENT
'CAUSE YOU'RE A MAN, WALT.

22:10.163 --> 22:15.749
SHERIFF? SHERIFF.
COME QUICK.

22:18.129 --> 22:19.994
WOMAN: YOU ARE NOT GETTING
BACK HERE WITHOUT ANY I.D.!

22:20.215 --> 22:21.455
DONNA: YOU DO NOT
SPEAK TO ME LIKE THAT!

22:21.674 --> 22:23.460
JUST CALM DOWN!
NO, YOU CALM DOWN!

22:23.676 --> 22:26.292
SHERIFF, THESE PEOPLE ARE
REFUSING TO SHOW ME ANY I.D.!

22:26.513 --> 22:28.128
YOU ARE RUDE
AND DISRESPECTFUL.

22:28.348 --> 22:30.930
EVERYONE, JUST TAKE IT EASY.
WHAT'S GOING ON HERE?

22:31.142 --> 22:32.803
DID YOU SEND
THESE PEOPLE DOWN HERE

22:33.019 --> 22:34.429
TO IDENTIFY
ED CRAWLEY'S BODY?

22:34.646 --> 22:37.058
IS THAT
WHAT THEY TOLD YOU?

22:37.273 --> 22:39.138
THEY SAY
THEY'RE RELATIVES.

22:39.359 --> 22:40.474
SHERIFF,
I'M REALLY SORRY,

22:40.693 --> 22:42.069
BUT DONNA
WANTED TO SEE THE BODY.

22:42.278 --> 22:43.358
AND I JUST THOUGHT MAYBE

22:43.571 --> 22:44.686
IT MIGHT PROVIDE HER
SOME KIND OF CLOSURE.

22:44.906 --> 22:46.521
FOR 20 YEARS,
WE'VE HAD THE IMAGE OF BLAIR

22:46.741 --> 22:48.151
LYING DEAD ON A SLAB,

22:48.368 --> 22:51.485
AND MAYBE IF WE CAN REPLACE THAT
WITH CRAWLEY ON A SLAB...

23:01.130 --> 23:05.840
YOU THINK THAT SEEING
YOUR DAUGHTER'S MURDERER

23:06.052 --> 23:09.670
WILL HELP THE ANGER
GO AWAY?

23:09.889 --> 23:12.881
I CAN TELL YOU
FROM PERSONAL EXPERIENCE,

23:13.101 --> 23:14.887
IT WON'T.

23:15.103 --> 23:17.139
ONLY TIME CAN DO THAT.

23:17.355 --> 23:19.562
REALLY?

23:19.774 --> 23:24.609
'CAUSE THE FIRST 20 YEARS
HAVEN'T MADE MUCH OF A DENT.

23:44.007 --> 23:47.795
IT'S REALLY
QUITE UNPLEASANT.

23:48.011 --> 23:50.172
ARE YOU SURE?
PLEASE, SHERIFF.

24:09.949 --> 24:13.533
[ SCREAMING ]
NO, NO, NO!

24:19.208 --> 24:21.540
[ SOBBING ]

24:23.713 --> 24:26.125
LONGMIRE: YOU THINK IRA CRAIG
COULD HAVE KILLED ED CRAWLEY?

24:26.341 --> 24:28.127
I THOUGHT CRAWLEY WAS KILLED
BY A BEAR.

24:28.343 --> 24:31.301
YEAH.
THAT'S THE THING -- HE WAS.

24:31.512 --> 24:33.093
BUT HE WAS IN RESTRAINTS
AT THE TIME,

24:33.306 --> 24:34.887
AND I THINK
THE BEAR WAS BAITED.

24:35.099 --> 24:37.511
YOU HAD A LOT OF CONTACT WITH
THE CRAIGS WHEN YOU WERE WARDEN.

24:37.727 --> 24:39.843
YOU THINK IRA COULD HAVE DONE
SOMETHING LIKE THAT?

24:40.063 --> 24:41.599
IRA? I DON'T KNOW.

24:41.814 --> 24:43.679
I THOUGHT YOU'D BE LEANING
TOWARDS THE MISSUS.
I WAS.

24:43.900 --> 24:46.812
BUT WHEN I SHOWED THEM THE BODY,
DONNA LOST IT.

24:47.028 --> 24:48.484
IRA JUST SEEMED AT PEACE,

24:48.696 --> 24:50.857
LIKE HE'D ALREADY HAD
HIS CLOSURE,

24:51.074 --> 24:53.360
LIKE HE'D ALREADY
SEEN CRAWLEY DEAD.

24:53.576 --> 24:55.737
I DON'T KNOW.
YOU GOT ANYBODY ELSE?

24:55.954 --> 24:58.036
HIS BROTHER-IN-LAW
DIDN'T SEEM TO LIKE HIM MUCH.

24:58.247 --> 24:59.748
YOU EVER RUN INTO HIM?

24:59.958 --> 25:01.573
NAH, I CAN'T REMEMBER
CRAWLEY'S FAMILY EVER VISITING.

25:01.793 --> 25:03.078
AS FOR THE CRAIGS,

25:03.294 --> 25:05.376
I CAN CERTAINLY SYMPATHIZE
WITH HOW THEY FELT

25:05.588 --> 25:08.455
SEEING THE GUY WHO KILLED
THEIR DAUGHTER WALKING FREE.

25:08.675 --> 25:11.132
THE CRAIGS SAID IF YOU'D HAVE
BEEN AT THE PAROLE HEARING,

25:11.344 --> 25:12.754
IT WOULD HAVE MADE
A DIFFERENCE.

25:12.971 --> 25:14.507
NOT REALLY.

25:14.722 --> 25:16.678
I WISH I HAD BEEN AT THE HEARING
INSTEAD OF THE NEW GUY.

25:16.891 --> 25:18.847
BUT THAT PAROLE BOARD
WAS CHARGED WITH SAVING MONEY.

25:19.060 --> 25:20.470
THEY WERE DETERMINED
TO RELEASE HIM.

25:20.687 --> 25:22.052
NOTHING I SAID
WOULD HAVE MATTERED.

25:22.271 --> 25:24.603
CRAWLEY'S PRISON RECORD
DID LOOK AWFULLY CLEAN.

25:24.816 --> 25:26.977
YES, IT WAS,
BUT A LOT OF GUYS THOUGHT

25:27.193 --> 25:28.649
THAT CRAWLEY HAD STABBED
AND KILLED A GUARD.

25:28.861 --> 25:31.477
RECORD SAID
HE WAS EXONERATED ON THAT.

25:31.698 --> 25:33.438
YEP, ANOTHER INMATE
TOOK CREDIT FOR IT.

25:33.658 --> 25:35.899
THEN AGAIN, HE WAS A LIFER.
HE HAD NOTHING TO LOSE.

25:36.119 --> 25:37.905
CRAWLEY COULD HAVE EASILY
BOUGHT HIM OUT

25:38.121 --> 25:40.407
WITH A COUPLE OF CARTONS
OF SMOKES TO TAKE THE FALL.

25:42.458 --> 25:43.834
I GOT TO SAY, DAN.

25:44.043 --> 25:46.250
IT MUST BE NICE
TO LEAVE THAT JOB BEHIND.

25:46.462 --> 25:47.918
THAT'S TRUE.

25:48.131 --> 25:50.998
ALTHOUGH I WOULD HAVE LIKED TO
HAVE GONE OUT ON MY OWN TERMS,

25:51.217 --> 25:53.458
RATHER THAN BEING PUSHED
INTO EARLY RETIREMENT

25:53.678 --> 25:54.508
DUE TO BUDGET CUTS.

25:54.721 --> 25:55.927
[ CHUCKLES ]

25:56.139 --> 25:58.846
I'M FAMILIAR
WITH BUDGET CUTS.

25:59.058 --> 26:00.719
THEY'RE TRYING TO REPLACE US
WITH COMPUTERS, WALT.

26:00.935 --> 26:02.141
I KNOW.

26:02.353 --> 26:04.514
NOTHING MORE VALUABLE
THAN MEMORY.

26:05.982 --> 26:08.689
SPEAKING OF WHICH,
MIND IF I BORROW YOURS?
SURE.

26:08.901 --> 26:10.516
I NEED YOU TO LOOK
AT THIS LIST --

26:10.737 --> 26:12.068
RECENTLY RELEASED
PRISONERS.

26:12.280 --> 26:14.191
IF YOU COULD IDENTIFY
WHETHER ANY OF THEM

26:14.407 --> 26:16.193
WERE CRAWLEY'S CELLMATES
OR ASSOCIATES.

26:16.409 --> 26:17.740
NO PROBLEM.

26:17.952 --> 26:19.567
MEANTIME, YOU GOT ANY
OF THOSE CAMPAIGN SIGNS

26:19.787 --> 26:21.038
IN THE BACK OF YOUR TRUCK?

26:21.247 --> 26:23.989
YEAH, BUT YOU DON'T
HAVE TO DO THAT. THAT'S --

26:24.208 --> 26:26.199
COME ON, WALT --
EVEN IF I DIDN'T LIKE YOU,

26:26.419 --> 26:28.831
I'D HATE TO SEE ANOTHER OLD PRO
BEING PUSHED OUT OF A JOB

26:29.047 --> 26:30.378
BY A YOUNG GUY.

26:30.590 --> 26:32.956
[LAUGHS]

26:33.176 --> 26:34.712
RUBY, I FOUND IT --

26:34.927 --> 26:37.304
THAT TACOMA THE VICTIM BORROWED
FROM HIS BROTHER-IN-LAW?

26:37.513 --> 26:39.799
I FOLLOWED IT TO A HOUSE
ON THE WEST SIDE.

26:40.016 --> 26:41.847
IT'S, UH,
PRETTY SHADY-LOOKING --

26:42.060 --> 26:43.641
NEWSPAPERS
IN THE WINDOWS --

26:43.853 --> 26:47.641
FERG, DO NOT EVEN THINK
ABOUT GOING IN THERE.

26:47.857 --> 26:49.393
DO NOT.
DON'T WORRY.

26:49.609 --> 26:51.019
I'M NOT GOING IN THERE
WITHOUT BACKUP, RUBY.

26:51.235 --> 26:52.441
WALT!

27:01.412 --> 27:05.325
YOU SEE ANY SIGNS OF A LAB --
BEAKERS, TEST TUBES, HOSES --

27:05.541 --> 27:07.281
YOU GET OUT --
THAT STUFF COULD BLOW.

27:07.502 --> 27:08.662
GOT IT.

27:18.721 --> 27:20.382
[GUN COCKS]

27:20.598 --> 27:24.216
[LAUGHTER]

27:25.603 --> 27:26.683
[ SCREAMS ]

27:46.332 --> 27:48.948
[GRUNTS]

27:58.719 --> 27:59.583
I STILL CAN'T GET THE SMELL
OF THAT PLACE OUT OF MY HEAD.

27:59.804 --> 28:01.214
IT WAS LIKE A WET DIAPER.

28:01.430 --> 28:03.216
WELL, THEY MIGHT BE
POOR HOUSEKEEPERS,

28:03.432 --> 28:05.263
BUT AT LEAST
THEY'RE THOUGHTFUL TWEAKERS.

28:05.476 --> 28:06.807
[ CHUCKLING ]
CHECK THIS OUT.

28:07.019 --> 28:11.012
"TO A SPECIAL UNCLE
ON HIS BIRTHDAY"?

28:11.232 --> 28:14.269
I THINK MY UNCLE WOULD PREFER
ONE OF THESE MAGAZINES.

28:14.485 --> 28:16.316
[ CHUCKLES ]
YEAH.

28:16.529 --> 28:18.565
HOW DO YOU KNOW
ED CRAWLEY?
I DON'T.

28:18.781 --> 28:21.568
YOU WERE SEEN
DRIVING HIS TRUCK.

28:21.784 --> 28:23.285
I TOLD YOU
I DON'T KNOW THAT GUY.

28:23.494 --> 28:24.825
WHERE DID YOU GET
THE TRUCK?

28:25.037 --> 28:28.120
I TOLD YOU, MAN.
SANTA GAVE IT TO ME.

28:28.332 --> 28:31.119
WHAT DOES YOUR SANTA ENTITY
LOOK LIKE?

28:31.335 --> 28:33.917
YOU DON'T SEE SANTA.

28:34.130 --> 28:35.290
AND THAT'S THE THING.

28:35.506 --> 28:37.747
HE COMES WHEN
YOU'RE SLEEPING, RIGHT?

28:37.967 --> 28:39.423
SO, WHILE I WAS SLEEPING,

28:39.635 --> 28:42.672
SOMEONE LEFT THE TRUCK
OUTSIDE THE HOUSE -- UNLOCKED,

28:42.889 --> 28:45.676
KEYS IN IT AND EVERYTHING.

28:45.892 --> 28:48.258
DO YOU KNOW WHO OWNS THAT HOUSE
YOU WERE CRASHING IN?

28:48.477 --> 28:50.468
PATCHES.

28:50.688 --> 28:51.803
WHAT'S PATCHES'
REAL NAME?

28:52.023 --> 28:53.103
I DON'T KNOW.

28:53.316 --> 28:55.932
HE'S JUST ALWAYS GOT
NICOTINE PATCHES ON.

28:56.152 --> 28:58.734
MAYBE...DAVE OR...DAN?

28:58.946 --> 29:00.732
CAN YOU GIVE ME A LIST
OF ALL THE PEOPLE

29:00.948 --> 29:02.688
WHO LIVE OR HANG OUT
AT PATCHES' HOUSE?

29:02.909 --> 29:04.649
SURE.

29:04.869 --> 29:07.360
PATCHES TURNS OUT TO BE A GUY
NAMED GREG PIERSON.

29:07.580 --> 29:10.242
LEASES THE HOUSE FROM A WOMAN
NAMED AMY STONESIFER.

29:10.458 --> 29:12.039
[ TOILET FLUSHES ]
LUCIAN:
I KNOW AMY STONESIFER.

29:12.251 --> 29:14.242
SHE LIVES AT THE HOME
I JUST GOT KICKED OUT OF.

29:14.462 --> 29:15.702
NUTTY AS A DRUNK MONKEY.

29:15.922 --> 29:17.537
THAT'S PRETTY SMART
FOR THEM DRUG COOKERS

29:17.757 --> 29:19.372
USING A SENILE OLD WOMAN
AS A LANDLORD.

29:19.592 --> 29:22.584
LUCIAN, DO YOU MIND?
WE GOT WORK TO DO.

29:22.803 --> 29:25.590
OH, THAT'S RIGHT, WALT.
OF COURSE. I FORGOT.

29:25.806 --> 29:28.218
YOU'RE TRYING TO WASTE MORE TIME
AND MONEY PUNISHING SOMEBODY

29:28.434 --> 29:30.425
DID SOCIETY A FAVOR
BY KILLING A SCUMBAG.

29:30.645 --> 29:32.181
AIN'T YOU GOT SOMEWHERE
YOU COULD BE RIGHT NOW?

29:32.396 --> 29:34.887
WELL, THE HIPPIES ARE
IN MY GUEST ROOM THERE.

29:37.276 --> 29:40.518
BRANCH, I GOT TWO
VERY IMPORTANT JOBS FOR YOU.

29:40.738 --> 29:43.696
FIRST, TWEAKER JOE GAVE ME
A BUNCH OF NAMES...

29:43.908 --> 29:45.899
OF GUYS WHO HANG OUT
AT THE METH HOUSE.

29:46.118 --> 29:48.029
PERVY STU?

29:48.246 --> 29:49.827
CHECK THE LIST OF NAMES
THE WARDEN GAVE US.

29:50.039 --> 29:51.745
SEE IF ANY OF THOSE
RECENTLY RELEASED PRISONERS

29:51.958 --> 29:53.539
HAVE NICKNAMES
THAT MATCH THESE.

29:53.751 --> 29:55.457
MAYBE ONE OF THESE METH HEADS
IS CONNECTED TO ED CRAWLEY.

29:55.670 --> 29:57.206
AND THE SECOND?

29:57.421 --> 29:58.957
YOU GOT TO GET
THE RETIREMENT HOME

29:59.173 --> 30:01.129
TO DROP THE CHARGES
AND TAKE LUCIAN BACK.

30:06.639 --> 30:08.345
AAH!

30:08.557 --> 30:10.422
H EY! H EY!

30:10.643 --> 30:11.849
HEY!

30:12.061 --> 30:14.268
AAH! SHERIFF!

30:14.480 --> 30:15.936
FERG,
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

30:16.148 --> 30:18.184
BRANCH, HELP FERG.

30:18.401 --> 30:20.813
OH, GOD.

30:21.028 --> 30:22.939
WHAT'S GOING ON
IN THERE?

30:32.581 --> 30:34.287
WALT.

30:34.500 --> 30:35.831
WE GET THIS A LOT.

30:36.043 --> 30:37.749
HE HAS ALL THE SYMPTOMS
OF A METHAMPHETAMINE OVERDOSE.

30:37.962 --> 30:39.668
THANK YOU.

30:41.966 --> 30:44.833
ALL THOSE GREETING CARDS
MUST HAVE BEEN LACED WITH METH.

30:45.052 --> 30:47.543
THERE WERE AT LEAST 100.
THAT'S A LOT OF PRODUCT.

30:47.763 --> 30:49.469
THAT'S MORE
THAN JUST CASUAL USE.

30:49.682 --> 30:51.798
THEY WERE DISTRIBUTING
OUT OF THAT HOUSE.

30:52.018 --> 30:54.600
BUT WHY DISTRIBUTE IN THAT FORM?
WHY NOT JUST SELL ROCKS?

30:54.812 --> 30:56.894
WHAT'S THE BEST WAY TO GET STUFF
IN AND OUT OF PRISON?

30:57.106 --> 31:00.098
[ LAUGHS] MAIL.
THAT'S A CLEVER SYSTEM.

31:00.318 --> 31:01.558
YEAH.

31:01.777 --> 31:04.393
PLACE METH
INTO GREETING CARDS.

31:04.613 --> 31:06.274
THE PRISONERS JUST CHEW IT UP
AND GET HIGH.

31:06.490 --> 31:07.650
AND IF THE METH HOUSE
WE RAIDED

31:07.867 --> 31:09.482
WAS PROVIDING DRUGS
TO THE PRISON...

31:09.702 --> 31:12.489
SOMEONE IN THAT HOUSE MUST HAVE
A CONNECTION TO THE PRISON.

31:12.705 --> 31:14.286
AND A CONNECTION
TO ED CRAWLEY.

31:14.498 --> 31:15.749
HEY, GUYS. LOOK.

31:15.958 --> 31:17.073
VIC, YOU --
YOU SHOULD BE IN BED.

31:17.293 --> 31:18.749
NO, SERIOUSLY,
YOU GOT TO SEE THIS.

31:18.961 --> 31:20.371
BRANCH:
WHAT DO THEY HAVE YOU ON?

31:20.588 --> 31:22.704
THIS IS WHERE
THE DART HIT ME.

31:24.216 --> 31:26.468
THIS IS FROM A SYRINGE.

31:26.677 --> 31:29.089
THE DART. SYRINGE.

31:29.305 --> 31:33.890
ED CRAWLEY'S HOLES LOOKED
LIKE THIS, NOT LIKE THIS.

31:34.101 --> 31:35.762
ED CRAWLEY
WASN'T SHOOTING UP DRUGS.

31:35.978 --> 31:37.718
HE WAS SHOT
WITH A TRANQUILIZER DART.

31:37.938 --> 31:40.520
[ SIGHS ] RESTRAINTS,
FLANK STEAK,

31:40.733 --> 31:42.189
ANIMAL TRANQUILIZERS.

31:42.401 --> 31:46.815
SOMEONE PLANNED THIS MURDER
VERY CAREFULLY.

31:47.031 --> 31:48.771
[ BREATHES HEAVILY ]

31:48.991 --> 31:50.982
DO ANY OF THESE
RELEASED PRISONERS

31:51.202 --> 31:53.193
STRIKE YOU
AS SOPHISTICATED ENOUGH

31:53.412 --> 31:56.700
TO PLAN EITHER
A METH-SMUGGLING OPERATION

31:56.916 --> 31:58.656
OR AN ELABORATE MURDER?

31:58.876 --> 32:02.414
THIS GUY, STEVEN KANE,
HE ACTED AS HIS OWN LAWYER.

32:02.630 --> 32:03.585
DID HE WIN?

32:05.174 --> 32:06.254
NO.

32:06.467 --> 32:07.923
[ LUCIAN LAUGHS ]

32:08.135 --> 32:12.219
YOU'RE GOING AT THIS ALL WRONG.
THIS MURDER WAS BRUTAL.

32:12.431 --> 32:14.046
TIE MEAT TO A MAN,
HAVE A BEAR EAT HIM --

32:14.266 --> 32:16.257
THAT'S TORTURE,
AND TORTURE IS VENGEANCE.

32:16.477 --> 32:18.968
VENGEANCE IS YOUR MOTIVE.

32:19.188 --> 32:21.600
CRAWLEY'S BROTHER-IN-LAW
DOESN'T HAVE MUCH OF AN ALIBI.

32:21.816 --> 32:23.602
AND HE'S A LICENSED HUNTER.
SO IS IRA CRAIG.

32:23.818 --> 32:25.979
THAT DUDE'S DEFINITELY
A CANDIDATE FOR VENGEANCE.

32:26.195 --> 32:29.403
FERG.

32:29.615 --> 32:31.230
CAN YOU READ THIS?

32:31.450 --> 32:32.690
UH...

32:34.286 --> 32:35.742
"STONESIFER"?

32:35.955 --> 32:37.320
A GUARD NAMED
JERRY STONESIFER

32:37.540 --> 32:39.121
SIGNED SOME OF
THESE RELEASE FORMS.

32:39.333 --> 32:41.324
SAME LAST NAME AS THE WOMAN
WHO OWNS THE METH HOUSE.

32:41.544 --> 32:43.910
HE WAS A GUARD AT THE PRISON.
HE WOULD HAVE KNOWN CRAWLEY.

32:44.130 --> 32:45.916
SO MAYBE CRAWLEY'S
BUDDY FROM PRISON WASN'T
ANOTHER PRISONER...

32:46.132 --> 32:47.588
BUT A PRISON GUARD.

32:47.800 --> 32:50.382
AND THEN CRAWLEY'S CAR
ENDS UP AT THE AUNT'S HOUSE.

32:50.594 --> 32:52.505
THAT'S ABOUT FOUR TOO MANY
COINCIDENCES FOR ME.

32:52.721 --> 32:53.881
LET'S BRING HIM IN.

32:54.098 --> 32:57.636
I FOUND HIM, WALT.
HE WAS RESISTING ARREST.

32:57.852 --> 32:59.342
HE DIDN'T SEEM TOO INTERESTED
IN TALKING!

32:59.562 --> 33:02.520
[GRUNTS, GROANS]

33:02.731 --> 33:06.098
SO, MR. STONESIFER...

33:06.318 --> 33:07.979
YOU WORKED AT THE PRISON
FOR EIGHT YEARS

33:08.195 --> 33:09.651
BEFORE YOU DEPARTED
IN FEBRUARY.

33:11.991 --> 33:17.281
MR. STONESIFER, DO YOU KNOW
A MAN NAMED ED CRAWLEY?

33:17.496 --> 33:18.611
LAWYER.

33:18.831 --> 33:20.662
I'LL TAKE THAT
AS A MAYBE.

33:20.875 --> 33:23.161
DID YOU CALL UP AND OFFER HIM
A JOB A COUPLE DAYS AGO?

33:23.377 --> 33:25.993
LAWYER.
UH-HUH.

33:26.213 --> 33:29.501
YOU, UH, IN POSSESSION OF ANY
KIND OF ANIMAL TRANQUILIZER?
LAWYER!

33:29.717 --> 33:31.673
HAVE YOU BEEN USING
YOUR AUNT'S HOUSE AS A BASE

33:31.886 --> 33:33.922
TO SMUGGLE METHAMPHETAMINE
INTO THE STATE PRISON?

33:34.138 --> 33:36.003
LAWYER!

33:40.728 --> 33:42.093
YOU SHOULD REALLY
THANK BRANCH.

33:42.313 --> 33:44.975
HE PERSUADED SNOWCAP VISTA
TO TAKE YOU BACK.

33:45.191 --> 33:46.931
NOW,
HOW DID HE DO THAT?

33:47.151 --> 33:48.937
APPARENTLY HE FOUND
SEVERAL CODE VIOLATIONS

33:49.153 --> 33:50.233
HE THREATENED TO REPORT

33:50.446 --> 33:51.686
UNLESS THEY LET YOU
BACK IN, SO...

33:51.906 --> 33:53.396
PROOF OF MY NEPHEW'S
SHADY ETHICS

33:53.616 --> 33:55.823
AND THE LENGTHS MY FAMILY
WILL GO TO GET RID OF ME.

33:56.035 --> 33:57.320
[ CHUCKLES ]

33:57.536 --> 33:59.527
ACTUALLY, I THINK
BRANCH KIND OF LIKES YOU.

33:59.747 --> 34:00.907
I DON'T TRUST BRANCH.

34:01.123 --> 34:02.499
AND MORE IMPORTANT,
I DON'T TRUST HIS DAD.

34:02.708 --> 34:04.039
MY BROTHER'S
A SON OF A BITCH.

34:04.251 --> 34:06.333
ALL HE WANTS IS TO SEE
HIS BOY WEARING YOUR BADGE.

34:06.545 --> 34:08.627
DON'T WORRY.
YOU BETTER BE.

34:08.839 --> 34:10.045
IF YOU'VE GOT
ANY SECRETS, WALT,

34:10.257 --> 34:11.372
YOU BEST BE READY
TO READ THEM IN THE PAPER.

34:11.592 --> 34:13.253
I THINK MOST
OF MY IMPORTANT SECRETS

34:13.469 --> 34:15.676
ARE KEPT DEEP ENOUGH.

34:15.888 --> 34:19.096
SO, WHAT'D YOU USED TO DO

34:19.308 --> 34:20.798
WHEN A SUSPECT
WOULDN'T TALK TO YOU?

34:21.018 --> 34:24.385
SIMPLE -- I'D WHUP HIS ASS
TILL HE DID TALK.

34:24.605 --> 34:25.811
[LAUGHS]

34:26.023 --> 34:28.184
WELL, WE CAN'T DO THAT
THESE DAYS.

34:28.400 --> 34:32.393
OH, LISTEN TO YOUR WHINING.
IT'S JUST SO SAD.

34:32.613 --> 34:35.195
I'D SHOOT A BUCK OUT OF SEASON
TO HAVE YOUR PROBLEMS.

34:35.407 --> 34:37.819
WHAT YOU GONNA DO
ABOUT A SUSPECT DON'T TALK?

34:38.035 --> 34:39.650
YOU'RE GONNA DO
SOME SHERIFFING.

34:39.870 --> 34:42.282
GOT TO DIG AROUND
A FEW GARBAGE CANS,

34:42.498 --> 34:45.285
ARREST SOME DRUNKS, DO SOME OF
THAT FANCY "CSI" STUFF,

34:45.501 --> 34:47.116
ANALYZE SOME BEAR SHIT.

34:56.512 --> 34:58.377
ARE YOU HERE
TO ARREST ME?

34:58.597 --> 35:00.462
I HAVEN'T DECIDED YET.

35:00.683 --> 35:03.265
I'M PRETTY SURE YOU DIDN'T SHOOT
VIC BY ACCIDENT.

35:03.477 --> 35:05.763
IF YOU WERE OUT THERE
TRYING TO TRANQUILIZE A BEAR,

35:05.980 --> 35:07.470
YOU'D HAVE USED
A BIGGER DOSAGE.

35:07.690 --> 35:09.021
BUT IF YOU WERE OUT THERE

35:09.233 --> 35:12.020
TRYING TO SLOW DOWN OMAR
AND MY DEPUTY,

35:12.236 --> 35:14.227
YOU'D HAVE USED
A SMALLER DOSAGE.

35:14.446 --> 35:17.313
MAKE SURE
YOU DIDN'T KILL THEM.

35:17.533 --> 35:22.323
OKAY. MAYBE I WENT
A LITTLE TOO FAR.

35:22.538 --> 35:25.371
BUT IF I DON'T STAND UP
FOR THESE BEARS, WHO WILL?

35:25.583 --> 35:27.699
IF I CAN JUST RELOCATE
WAFFLES, OKAY,

35:27.918 --> 35:29.704
AWAY FROM HUMAN
POPULATIONS --

35:29.920 --> 35:33.333
I NOTICE YOU'RE NOT DEFENDING
WAFFLES' INNOCENCE ANYMORE.

35:33.549 --> 35:35.380
YEAH, WELL -- YEAH.

35:35.593 --> 35:37.083
WHICH MEANS YOU MUST HAVE DONE
YOUR TESTS ON WAFFLES

35:37.303 --> 35:40.716
AND REALIZE SHE DID CONSUME
SOME HUMAN FLESH.

35:40.931 --> 35:43.013
I DON'T GET IT, SHERIFF.

35:43.225 --> 35:46.217
IT JUST DOESN'T FIT
HER PROFILE.

35:46.437 --> 35:49.224
WELL...
[GRUNTS]

35:49.440 --> 35:52.853
I DON'T THINK IT WAS HER IDEA
TO KILL THAT GUY, PETE.

35:53.068 --> 35:55.275
NOW...

35:55.487 --> 35:57.102
IF YOU CAN
JUST PROMISE ME

35:57.323 --> 36:00.565
THAT YOU WON'T SHOOT ANY MORE
PEOPLE WITH THAT GUN OF YOURS,

36:00.784 --> 36:02.775
I NEED HELP
WITH A COUPLE OF THINGS.

36:02.995 --> 36:04.405
SURE.

36:04.622 --> 36:06.328
I NEED TO KNOW
IF JERRY STONESIFER

36:06.540 --> 36:08.747
OR ANYBODY ELSE EVER CALLED IN
OR STOPPED BY

36:08.959 --> 36:11.291
FOR INFORMATION ON
AGGRESSIVE BEARS IN THE AREA.

36:11.503 --> 36:14.495
I CAN CHECK OUR RECORDS.
WHAT'S THE OTHER THING?

36:18.761 --> 36:22.629
IF YOU TESTED WAFFLES' FUR
FOR ISOTOPES,

36:22.848 --> 36:25.840
THAT ONLY MEANS ONE THING.

36:26.060 --> 36:28.472
YOU HAVE THAT BEAR.

36:38.697 --> 36:40.858
[ VEHICLE APPROACHES ]

36:52.169 --> 36:55.832
[TRUCK DOOR OPENS ]

36:57.925 --> 37:00.632
HELLO, DAN.

37:00.844 --> 37:03.130
WHAT THE HELL
YOU GOT THERE, WALT?

37:03.347 --> 37:05.338
A BEAR.

37:05.557 --> 37:07.843
WHY'D YOU
BRING HIM UP HERE?

37:08.060 --> 37:09.641
I'M TAKING HER NORTH.

37:09.853 --> 37:11.844
I THOUGHT
I'D STOP BY ON THE WAY.

37:12.064 --> 37:14.680
I WANTED TO TALK TO YOU
ABOUT JERRY STONESIFER.

37:14.900 --> 37:17.892
HE'S A GOOD GUY --
TROUBLED, BUT HE'S A GOOD GUY.

37:18.112 --> 37:19.101
TROUBLED?

37:19.321 --> 37:21.528
DRUGS. IT HAPPENS.

37:21.740 --> 37:24.607
THE GUARDS GET LOCKED IN
WITH THE GENERAL POPULATION,
BAD THINGS HAPPEN.

37:24.827 --> 37:26.738
NOTHING IN STONESIFER'S RECORD
ABOUT THAT.

37:26.954 --> 37:28.865
WELL, LIKE I SAID,
HE'S A GOOD GUY,

37:29.081 --> 37:31.868
AND I DIDN'T THINK IT WAS FAIR
OF ME TO RUIN HIS LIFE,

37:32.084 --> 37:33.995
SO I JUST ENCOURAGED HIM
TO RESIGN.

37:34.211 --> 37:35.917
WHY ARE YOU ASKING
ABOUT JERRY?

37:36.130 --> 37:38.212
I THINK HE HELPED YOU
KILL ED CRAWLEY.

37:38.424 --> 37:41.086
[SIGHS] ME?

37:41.301 --> 37:42.427
YEP.

37:42.636 --> 37:43.967
ARE YOU MESSING WITH ME,
SHERIFF?

37:44.179 --> 37:45.294
NOPE.

37:45.514 --> 37:46.720
A BEAR KILLED ED CRAWLEY.

37:46.932 --> 37:48.342
THIS BEAR. I KNOW.

37:48.559 --> 37:50.595
THE BEAR WAS JUST A WEAPON.
YOU GUYS KILLED HIM.

37:50.811 --> 37:54.019
STONESIFER CALLED UP ED CRAWLEY
AND TOLD HIM ABOUT A JOB.

37:54.231 --> 37:56.893
WHEN HE ARRIVED, YOU SHOT HIM
WITH TRANQUILIZER DARTS,

37:57.109 --> 37:59.475
THEN YOU TIED HIM UP TO A TREE
WITH MEAT ON HIM

37:59.695 --> 38:01.276
S0 A BEAR
WOULD COME MAUL HIM.

38:01.488 --> 38:04.150
THAT'S GONNA BE
PRETTY HARD TO PROVE.

38:04.366 --> 38:07.153
I NEVER BOUGHT
ANY ANIMAL TRANQUILIZER.

38:07.369 --> 38:09.530
NEVER EVEN CALLED
ED CRAWLEY.

38:09.747 --> 38:12.159
IT'S POSSIBLE
STONESIFER DID ALL THAT STUFF,

38:12.374 --> 38:13.750
BUT IT WAS ON YOUR ORDERS.

38:13.959 --> 38:16.371
I'M GUESSING HE OWED YOU
FOR NOT FIRING HIM

38:16.587 --> 38:19.750
WHEN YOU DISCOVERED HE WAS
SMUGGLING METH INTO THE PRISON.

38:19.965 --> 38:21.705
YOU LET HIM RESIGN
ON A PARTIAL PENSION.

38:21.925 --> 38:24.541
YOU KNOW, SHERIFF,
I AIN'T NO LAWYER,

38:24.762 --> 38:27.003
AND CLEARLY YOU AREN'T,
EITHER,

38:27.222 --> 38:29.554
BECAUSE THAT'S ABOUT
THE MOST...

38:29.767 --> 38:31.632
CIRCUMSTANTIAL,

38:31.852 --> 38:33.012
SPECULATIVE ACCUSATION

38:33.228 --> 38:35.480
EVER DRUMMED UP
IN THE STATE OF WYOMING.

38:35.689 --> 38:36.849
YOU GOT NOTHING ON ME.

38:37.065 --> 38:37.975
THINK FAST.

38:38.192 --> 38:39.682
AAH!
WHAT THE HELL?!

38:39.902 --> 38:41.893
[ BEAR GROWLS ]
NOW I GOT SOMETHING
ON YOU --

38:42.112 --> 38:44.068
THE SCENT OF BEEF,
OF BLOOD,

38:44.281 --> 38:47.318
WHICH IS A SMELL
THAT WAFFLES HERE KNOWS WELL.

38:47.534 --> 38:50.150
SO HERE'S THE DEAL --
YOU TELL ME THAT YOU DID...

38:50.370 --> 38:53.282
WHAT I KNOW YOU DID...

38:53.499 --> 38:55.785
AND I WON'T UNLOCK
THIS CAGE.

38:56.001 --> 38:57.332
YOU'RE CRAZY.

38:57.544 --> 38:59.080
THERE'S A LOT OF THAT
GOING AROUND LATELY.

39:00.631 --> 39:01.916
YOU WENT TO
THE ABSAROKA BEAR INSTITUTE

39:02.132 --> 39:03.633
TO CHECK ON COLLARED BEARS,

39:03.842 --> 39:06.629
AND YOU FOUND ONE THAT ALREADY
HAD TWO LIVESTOCK KILLS.

39:06.845 --> 39:08.051
SO YOU HAD TO BE SURE

39:08.263 --> 39:10.049
AND TIE ED CRAWLEY
UP CLOSE TO THIS BEAR.

39:10.265 --> 39:12.176
AND KNOWING WAFFLES' TASTE
FOR BEEF,

39:12.392 --> 39:14.098
YOU COVERED HIM
IN FLANK STEAK.

39:14.311 --> 39:18.930
YOU'RE DOING ALL THIS
FOR CRAWLEY?

39:19.149 --> 39:22.767
THAT PIECE OF GARBAGE?

39:22.986 --> 39:26.228
THAT ANIMAL KILLED
ONE OF MY GUARDS

39:26.448 --> 39:29.030
AND SLAUGHTERED
THE CRAIGS' ONLY DAUGHTER.

39:29.243 --> 39:32.280
AND NOW YOU ARE COMING OUT HERE
AND THREATENING ME?

39:32.496 --> 39:34.487
[ BEAR GROWLS ]

39:34.706 --> 39:37.118
YOU OPEN THAT THING, YOU'RE
IN AS MUCH DANGER AS I AM.

39:37.334 --> 39:40.576
MOST BEARS CAN RUN MORE
THAN 30 MILES AN HOUR.

39:40.796 --> 39:42.286
BUT YOU KNOW THE OLD JOKE.

39:42.506 --> 39:46.090
MAYBE I CAN'T OUTRUN THIS BEAR,
BUT I CAN OUTRUN YOU.

39:47.302 --> 39:50.635
SO, YOU TELL ME THAT YOU DID
WHAT I KNOW YOU DID.

39:50.848 --> 39:51.803
COME ON, WALT.

39:54.268 --> 39:55.633
OKAY, OKAY, OKAY!

39:55.853 --> 39:57.684
OKAY.

39:57.896 --> 40:00.103
JUST DO ME
TWO FAVORS, WALT.

40:00.315 --> 40:02.021
THAT YOU'RE GONNA LEAVE JERRY
OUT OF THIS.

40:02.234 --> 40:03.599
HE DIDN'T KNOW ANYTHING.

40:03.819 --> 40:05.559
HE THOUGHT WE WERE JUST GONNA
HAZE CRAWLEY A LITTLE BIT.

40:05.779 --> 40:07.690
WHAT'S THE SECOND FAVOR?

40:07.906 --> 40:10.238
I WANT TOMMY LEE JONES
TO PLAY ME IN THE MOVIE

40:10.450 --> 40:12.577
BECAUSE PEOPLE
ARE GONNA SEE ME AS A HERO.

40:12.786 --> 40:14.993
BECAUSE I AM A HERO.

40:15.205 --> 40:18.413
I'M A 55-YEAR-OLD GUY
WHO WAS PUSHED ASIDE

40:18.625 --> 40:20.456
WITH A LOUSY
LITTLE PENSION.

40:20.669 --> 40:22.079
BUT I DIDN'T GO QUIETLY.

40:22.296 --> 40:25.459
I'M A GUY WHO DIDN'T SIT THERE
AND DO NOTHING

40:25.674 --> 40:27.835
WHILE A MURDERER
WALKED FREE.

40:28.051 --> 40:29.166
MY FRIEND GOT DEATH.

40:29.386 --> 40:31.422
THE CRAIGS
GOT A LIFETIME SENTENCE

40:31.638 --> 40:34.880
OF NEVER SEEING THEIR DAUGHTER
AGAIN BECAUSE OF CRAWLEY.

40:35.100 --> 40:37.807
AND IF THAT
SON OF A BITCH

40:38.020 --> 40:40.887
GETS TORN APART BY A BEAR
LIMB TO LIMB,

40:41.106 --> 40:42.721
I WILL WATCH THAT MOVIE.

40:42.941 --> 40:45.978
AND BY GOD,
I'LL GO BACK AND SEE IT AGAIN.

40:46.194 --> 40:47.525
THIS AIN'T A MOVIE.

40:47.738 --> 40:49.729
WE CAN'T BE TORTURING
AND MURDERING PEOPLE

40:49.948 --> 40:53.532
NO MATTER HOW RIGHT
WE THINK WE ARE.

40:53.744 --> 40:55.735
SOMEBODY'S GOT TO BE
THE SHERIFF,

40:55.954 --> 40:57.945
OR ELSE WE'RE ALL
JUST ANIMALS.

40:58.165 --> 41:02.875
WHAT THE WORLD NEEDS
IS MORE HUMAN BEINGS.

41:08.508 --> 41:12.376
NOW, WAFFLES, TECHNICALLY,
AFTER THREE STRIKES,

41:12.596 --> 41:15.383
WE'RE SUPPOSED TO
SHOOT YOU.

41:15.599 --> 41:19.592
BUT WE HUMANS HAVE THIS THING
CALLED ENTRAPMENT.

41:19.811 --> 41:23.599
NOW, IT'S HARD TO EXPLAIN,
BUT...YOU JUST PROMISE

41:23.815 --> 41:27.899
THAT YOU'LL STAY AS FAR AWAY
FROM TOWN AS YOU CAN.

41:28.111 --> 41:30.193
[MUSIC]

41:30.405 --> 41:32.691
OKAY, THEN.

41:44.836 --> 41:47.578
[MUSIC CONTINUES]
